snippet.title: 𝕋𝕙𝕖 𝕊𝕖𝕥𝕥𝕝𝕖𝕞𝕖𝕟𝕥
snippet.description:
Always remember - this is The Settlement, we are not part of your YT "Communities" and we have our own rules.

Our spot to kick back,smoke some things, and talk with friends. Dabs and beef whenever I want to have fun. This started with just one show a week, now we have regular shows for Monday Mayhem @ 9:15pm, WTF Wednesday @ 10:00pm, and Fkn Fun Friday @ 9:15pm! Also, we enjoy some impromptu Lives so make sure you are *subscribed and turn the notification bell on* so you don't miss out because ish keeps getting better.  Thanks for coming

Also, for the record , this is all me and my opinions.  Don't cry to other people or blame them for my words/actions. If ya gunna come play, come with ya real accts (Don't be like flounder kids, it's not a good look)because no one has time for the boring trolls and spamming.🖕🤣
